NAME
       foomatic-addpjloptions   -   Edit  PJL  options  into  the
       foomatic database

SYNOPSIS
       foomatic-addpjloptions [OPTION]...

       foomatic-addpjlop­
       tions[ -f ] [ -i ]-p<printer ID> [ <pjl option file> ]
       foomatic-addpjloptions-h


Description
       foomatic-addpjloptions adds the PJL options  listed  by  a
       printer  to the Foomatic database. The option list is read
       from a file if specified or else from standard input.

       The appropriate printer ID must be provided through option
       -p.


   Options
       -p<printer ID>
                 Printer where to add the PJL options

                 <pjl option file> File with PJL options returned
                 by the printer. If this  filename  is  not  pro­
                 vided,  the  PJL options are taken from standard
                 input.

                 -f Force adding PJL options, no questions.

                 -i Add the most important PJL options only.

                 -h Print a help message


FILES
       foomatic-templates/pjl*.xml
                                Necessary for  successful  opera­
                                tion.


EXIT STATUS
       foomatic-addpjloptions returns ...

